43 covered persons.
44 (2) Compensation to persons involved in utilization review shall not contain any
45 direct or indirect incentives for them to make any particular review decisions.
46 (3) Compensation to utilization reviewers shall not be directly or indirectly based
47 on the number or type of noncertifications they render.
